Finance Associate, Magic Circle Firm, Dubai
Finance Associate, Magic Circle Firm, Dubai
Location:  --Dubai
This Magic Circle firm with an outstanding client base is looking for a junior (2-3  PQE) lawyer for their Dubai office.
The role will be a great opportunity to work a range matters in the team covering different types of high quality work. For this role experience in asset finance is essential as is a solid grounding in general finance transactions.
The successful candidate will have excellent academics and have experience of working at another Magic Circle/top US firm.
Should you wish to apply for this role, please contact Richard McLerie by sending your cv through to richard@jlegal.com.
